# Privacy Policy / Политика конфиденциальности

**Freedge**
Last updated / Последнее обновление: April 2026

---

## English

### Information We Collect
Freedge uses your device camera to take photos of your fridge contents. These photos are sent to Groq API to generate recipe suggestions.

We do not collect, store, or share any personal information. Photos are processed temporarily and are not stored on our servers.

### Camera Permission
We request camera access solely to capture photos of your fridge for recipe generation. We do not use the camera for any other purpose.

### Third-Party Services
Freedge uses Groq API (groq.com) for AI-powered recipe generation. Photos are sent to Groq servers for processing. Please review Groq's privacy policy at https://groq.com/privacy-policy

### Data Storage
- Photos are stored locally on your device only
- Recipe history is stored locally on your device
- We do not have access to your data

### Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: freedge.app@gmail.com

